vulnerabilities.suggested_fix:
In the `merge` function, update the `ownership_change` of the destination token to the current block number. This ensures that the resulting merged token is also subject to the flash-vote restriction.

```solidity
// Inside merge function, after updating locked[_to]
ownership_change[_to] = block.number;
```

Similarly, if `multiSplit` is enabled, ensure new tokens also have `ownership_change` set to `block.number`.
